	that with the BB-enabled CCI mitigation approach, by setting the
	interference threshold parameter to an optimal value, a gain of up
	to 40% in sum throughput can be achieved compared to uncoordinated
	random medium access in such ad hoc networks. Moreover, it is demonstrated
